     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap IMMZ.D.ConceptMap</b></p><a name=\"IMMZ.D.ConceptMap\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZ.D.ConceptMap\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html\">IMMZ.D CodeSystem for Data Elements</a> to <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-event-status.html\">EventStatus</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>DE2 (Completed)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>completed</td></tr><tr><td>DE3 (Entered in error)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>entered-in-error</td></tr><tr><td>DE4 (Not done)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>not-done</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-event-status.html\">EventStatus</a> to <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html\">IMMZ.D CodeSystem for Data Elements</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>completed</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE2 (Completed)</td></tr><tr><td>entered-in-error</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE3 (Entered in error)</td></tr><tr><td>not-done</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE4 (Not done)</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 3 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html\">IMMZ.D CodeSystem for Data Elements</a> to <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-adverse-event-outcome.html\">AdverseEventOutcome</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>DE116 (Died)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>fatal</td></tr><tr><td>DE117 (Recovered)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>resolved</td></tr><tr><td>DE118 (Recovered with sequelae)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>resolvedWithSequelae</td></tr><tr><td>DE119 (Recovering)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>recovering</td></tr><tr><td>DE120 (Not recovered)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ongoing</td></tr><tr><td>DE121 (Unknown)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>unknown</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 4 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-adverse-event-outcome.html\">AdverseEventOutcome</a> to <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html\">IMMZ.D CodeSystem for Data Elements</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>fatal</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equi